[[Image:Drafting table.jpg|thumb|upright=1.1|Table d'architecte]]
Les écoles d'architecture les plus réputées aux États-Unis sont ([http://architecture.about.com/gi/dynamic/offsite.htm?zi=1/XJ&sdn=architecture&zu=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.di.net%2Farticle.php%3Farticle_id%3D178 source]) :
* [[Harvard]] [http://www.gsd.harvard.edu/ Graduate School of Design] ;
* [[Cal Poly]], [[San Luis Obispo]], [http://www.caed.calpoly.edu/ College of Architecture and Environmental Design] ;
* [[Université de Cincinnati]], [http://www.daap.uc.edu/ Design, Architecture, Art and Planning] ;
* [[Université Cornell]], [http://www.aap.cornell.edu/ College of Architecture, Art and Planning] ;
* [[Yale]], [http://www.yale.edu/academics/interim_architecture School of Architecture] ;
* [[Université du Texas]] à [[Austin (Texas)|Austin]], [http://web.austin.utexas.edu/architecture/ School of Architecture] ;
* Université d'État du [[Kansas]], [http://www.capd.ksu.edu/ College of Architecture, Planning and Design] ;
* [[Université du Michigan]], [http://www.tcaup.umich.edu/acadpgm/acad.html TAUBMAN COLLEGE Architecture and Urban Planning] ;
* [[Université de Pennsylvanie]], [http://www.design.upenn.edu/index.php School of Design] ;
* [[Université Columbia]], [[New York]], [http://www.arch.columbia.edu/ Graduate School of Architecture, Planning and Preservation];
* [[Florida International University]], [[Miami]], [http://www.fiu.edu/~soa FIU School of Architecture].

